name: [FSX] FedEx A300-600F Sunset Landing in Calgary ᴴᴰ
description:
Hey everybody, this is my 300th upload on YouTube, and what better way to celebrate 300 uploads with a video of... An A300! :) I thought I would make this FSX video, since I don't have any A300 footage at the moment :/ This is also my first FSX video with REX 4, a texture pack for FSX that greatly enhances the textures of pretty much everything in the sim. Hope you enjoy, and stay tuned for a 747 tomorrow ;)

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
